Package org.chocosolver.solver.constraints.binary

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PropAbsolute
    Enforces X = |Y|
    PropDistanceXYC
    | X - Y | op C
    op = {"==", "<", ">", "=/="}
    PropEqualX_Y
    X = Y Ensures Arc-Consistency
    PropEqualX_YC
    X = Y + C
    PropEqualXY_C
    X + Y = C
    PropGreaterOrEqualX_Y
    X >= Y
    PropGreaterOrEqualX_YC
    X >= Y + C
    PropGreaterOrEqualXY_C
    X + Y >= C
    PropLessOrEqualXY_C
    X + Y <= C
    PropNotEqualX_Y
    A specific Propagator extension defining filtering algorithm for:
    X =/= Y
    where X and Y are Variable objects.
    PropNotEqualX_YC
    A specific Propagator extension defining filtering algorithm for:
    X =/= Y + C
    where X and Y are Variable objects and C a constant.
    PropNotEqualXY_C
    A specific Propagator extension defining filtering algorithm for:
    X + Y =/= C
    where X and Y are Variable objects and C a constant.
    PropScale
    Scale propagator : ensures x * y = z With y a constant greater than one Ensures AC
    PropSquare
    Enforces X = Y^2
